metadata.name: Deep Blu Founders Pass #1
metadata.description: Get lifetime access to the most powerful NFT analytics tool available which includes real-time listings, live feeds, social intelligence, heatmaps, advanced technical analysis charts, crypto view, educational resources, actionable insights and so much more. Deep Blu holders also get free access to all new features and updates. In addition, Deep Blu holders will enjoy access to a private discord community where they can network with other traders, share hot tips, trade setups and more.
